OL,3,C30 years on: First woman priest
OL,4,Creflects on historic moment
OL,6,FIn March 1994, the first women priests
OL,7,Fin the Church of England were ordained
OL,8,Fat Bristol Cathedral.
OL,10,FThe first of them, because she came
OL,11,Ffirst alphabetically, was Angela
OL,12,FBerners-Wilson, then a chaplain at the
OL,13,FUniversity of Bristol.
OL,15,FIt was a monumental moment in the
OL,16,Fhistory of the Church and one she had
OL,17,Fcampaigned for, being a member of the
OL,18,FMovement for the Ordination of Women
OL,19,Ffor many years.
