OL,3,C30 years on: First woman priest
OL,4,Creflects on historic moment
OL,6,FNow 69-years-old and retired, she's
OL,7,Freflected on a time that was
OL,8,Frevolutionary and controversial.
OL,10,FShe said: "There were 32 of us
OL,11,Fordained together and no one is
OL,12,Fordained until the final amen is said
OL,13,Fat the end of the service. I was the
OL,14,Ffirst to step forward because my name
OL,15,Fbegan with B.
OL,17,F"It was very very special and very
OL,18,Fexciting and it's a day I will never
OL,19,Fforget".
