OL,3,C30 years on: First woman priest
OL,4,Creflects on historic moment
OL,6,FThere was no social media in those
OL,7,Fdays - if there had been, no doubt
OL,8,FAngela would have faced a huge
OL,9,Fbacklash from critics of the move. She
OL,10,Fdid, however face criticism in letter
OL,11,Fform.
OL,13,FAngela said: "I got about 300 letters
OL,14,Fand most of them were really
OL,15,Fsupportive and people were really
OL,16,Fthrilled. One or two of them were anti
OL,17,Fand one or two were really weird."
