OL,3,C30 years on: First woman priest
OL,4,Creflects on historic moment
OL,6,FAngela went on to become a chaplain at
OL,7,Fthe University of Bath and was made a
OL,8,Fprebendary of Wells Cathedral - a
OL,9,Fsenior role in the Church - in 2009.
OL,11,FIn 2016 she was appointed rector of
OL,12,Fthe Quantock Towers benefice in
OL,13,FSomerset, which is made up of eight
OL,14,Fchurches.
OL,16,FHer husband, Andrew Sillett, passed
OL,17,Faway during the Covid pandemic. Angela
OL,18,Ffelt the only thing to do was to keep
OL,19,Fworking, which she did until her
OL,20,Fretirement at the age of 68.
