OL,3,C30 years on: First woman priest
OL,4,Creflects on historic moment
OL,6,FIt is ironic that, now Angela has
OL,7,Fretired and has settled in Westbury on
OL,8,FTrym in Bristol, her local parish
OL,9,Fchurch was once one of those that
OL,10,Frejected the ordination of women.
OL,12,FAngela has played a part from the very
OL,13,Fstart in encouraging other women into
OL,14,Fministry.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
