OL,3,C30 years on: First woman priest
OL,4,Creflects on historic moment
OL,6,FWomen now make up nearly a third of
OL,7,Fthe 20,000 clergy in the Church of
OL,8,FEngland. It took another 20 years
OL,9,Fbefore they could become bishops.
OL,10,FHowever, it is still possible for a
OL,11,Fchurch to refuse to appoint a woman as
OL,12,Fpriest in 2024.
OL,14,FNow in her spare time, Angela supports
OL,15,Fthe Ukrainian Hub set up at the local
OL,16,FMethodist Church.
