OL,3,C30 years on: First woman priest
OL,4,Creflects on historic moment
OL,6,FShe said: "I think the world's
OL,7,Fprobably more insecure than it has
OL,8,Fbeen in my lifetime. So I hope people
OL,9,Fwill look to the church this Easter
OL,10,Fand come to church and receive some
OL,11,Fmessage of hope and comfort."
